Available Tools: share_file | set_permissions | get_shared_link | revoke_access | list_collaborators
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "file_id": "string", "user_email": "string", "permission": "view|comment|edit", "expires_at": "string" }
Response Schema: { "file_id": "string", "shared_link": "string", "collaborators": [{ "email": "string", "permission": "string" }] }
---
Question: Share the Q3 financial report with sarah.jenkins@corp.com and give her edit access until the end of the month.
Call: { "func_call": "share_file", "file_id": "fin_q3_2023_v4.xlsx", "user_email": "sarah.jenkins@corp.com", "permission": "edit", "expires_at": "2023-10-31T23:59:59Z" }
Response: { "file_id": "fin_q3_2023_v4.xlsx", "shared_link": "https://storage.corp.com/s/x9k2m-plq", "collaborators": [{ "email": "sarah.jenkins@corp.com", "permission": "edit" }] }

Question: I need to let the design team view the new logo assets without making changes; send access to mike@design.co valid for one week.
Call: { "func_call": "set_permissions", "file_id": "brand_assets_logo_v2.zip", "user_email": "mike@design.co", "permission": "view", "expires_at": "2023-11-15T12:00:00Z" }
Response: { "file_id": "brand_assets_logo_v2.zip", "shared_link": "https://storage.corp.com/s/b7n4x-zzt", "collaborators": [{ "email": "mike@design.co", "permission": "view" }] }

